    "title": "文化影响",
    "page_range": "4",
    "summary": "This section answers questions regarding the cultural foundations, conceptual boundaries, and evolving classification of \"二次元\" (2D/ACG) media.\n- Topics & Entities: Covers the relationship between \"二次元\" and \"ACGN\"; the influence of Japanese anime, manga, games, and light novels; the categorization of mobile games; and the recognition role of the \"二次元\" player community.\n- Definitions: Clarifies that \"二次元\" refers to a cultural attribute rather than a specific work genre, and distinguishes it from \"ACGN\" despite their frequent interchangeable use.\n- Claims: States that Japanese cultural products drive the close link between 二次元 and ACGN. Notes that some games initially excluded from the 二次元 category have shifted toward its cultural traits through iterative updates and are now accepted as \"二次元 mobile games\" by the player base.\n- Dates, Procedures, Tables, Figures, Metrics, Evidence Types: Contains no specific dates, procedural steps, quantitative metrics, tables, figures, or formal evidence types."
