    "summary": "This section addresses questions regarding player segmentation and product classification in the ACG mobile gaming sector. It covers:\n- **Topics & Entities:** Player demographics (“core ACG players” vs. “casual/broad ACG players”) and “ACG mobile games.”\n- **Definitions & Claims:** Distinguishes player types based on affinity for ACG culture and willingness to invest time and money. Clarifies that while the report’s ACG mobile games align with these traits, meeting them alone does not automatically classify a product as such. Provides an alternative report-applicable definition: mobile games primarily targeting core ACG players qualify as ACG mobile games.\n- **Dates:** 2025 (report copyright/context year).\n- **Procedures, Tables, Figures, Metrics, Evidence Types:** Not covered in this section."
